Introduction
Welcome to the Privacy Policy of the Aussie Family Lawyer Assistant. This policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you interact with our AI legal assistant. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency in our data handling practices.

Information Collection

Personal Information: We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us, including but not limited to your name, contact details, and any specific legal queries or circumstances.
Usage Data: We gather anonymous data regarding your interaction with our assistant, such as query types, timestamps, and frequency of use.
Use of Information

Service Provision: Your information is used to provide personalized legal information and assistance relevant to Australian Family Law.
Improvement of Services: We analyze usage data to enhance our assistant's accuracy, responsiveness, and overall user experience.
Legal Compliance: We may use your information to comply with applicable laws and regulations.
Disclosure of Information

Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.
Service Providers: We may share your data with trusted third parties who provide services on our behalf, such as data analysis or technical support. These parties are obligated not to disclose or use it for other purposes.
Data Security

We implement robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
Your Privacy Rights

You have the right to access, amend, or delete your personal information that we hold. Please contact us if you wish to exercise these rights.
Children's Privacy

Our service is not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from minors.
Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
